# Project: Meddollina 3D image-to-3D plugin

Single 2D image → high-fidelity 3D mesh for SETV Global's Meddollina.ai platform.

Pipeline: SAM 2 foreground isolation → TRELLIS.2 image-to-3D → Blender mesh cleanup → GLB export.

Stack: Python 3.11, `reconstruction_3d.py` (standalone module), FastAPI adapter, React + Three.js viewer.

Rules:
- AI-generated geometry must be labeled in API responses and UI (disclaimer field).
- Type hints are mandatory. Errors raise explicitly — never swallowed silently.
- `/shared/schemas` is the source of truth for API contracts.
- Inference requires NVIDIA GPU (24GB+ VRAM); develop on laptop, run pipeline on RunPod.
